  "industry_note": "UNS N07208 / Haynes 282 — modern γ' precipitation-strengthened wrought Ni superalloy (Ni bal, Cr 19-20, Co 10, Mo 8.5, Al 1.5, Ti 2.1, Fe ≤1.5 max, B 0.005, C 0.06). Better creep + weldability than Waspaloy / R-41 / 263 (lower γ' vol fraction → no strain-age cracking). Tmax 1149°C. 가장 advanced wrought Ni superalloy (2005 개발) — supercritical CO2 power cycle (Allam cycle), 항공 LPT casing, 가스 터빈 transition piece. AM LPBF: σy 623-915 (as-built/aged)."
